{"tid":1919352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿特首籲勿外遊 縱橫遊袁振寧：咁危險不如關閉機場","createTime":"2020-03-10T17:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T17:50:41.000Z","uid":105567,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4e4ad587a17e971aa3ea9888c8f0d41b4275a7","tid":1919352,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎在全球擴散，特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前見記者，預告會擴大封關，並呼籲香港居民如非必要不要外遊。縱橫遊常務董事袁振寧回應時質疑有關言論，更直言「如這樣危險，倒不如叫政府關閉機場吧」。<br />\n<br />\n袁振寧表示，不明白為何只有航空及旅遊業是高危，反問「乘坐港鐵、巴士等公共交通工具又如何？戲院，娛樂場所教會，食市，商場，室內活動應該一同呼籲」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1219393/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8A-%E7%B8%B1%E6%A9%AB%E9%81%8A%E8%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E5%AF%A7-%E5%92%81%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219393%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%258A-%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A7-%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=eff10975\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219393%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%258A-%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A7-%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E6%25A9%